    <S id="S_5">
        <FORM>watah kura matu’asay sa kura taywan a minengneng tu nika sainaneng sa kuya matu’asay a tatusa mipitau paluma’ tuya kudasing sa.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh"> 「哇塞，這些老人家！」 那個台灣人看到這二位老人家如此能幹的（用鋤頭）種植花生。</TRANSL>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="en"> ‘Wow, the old people!’ The Taiwanese saw the old couple work hard to grow peanuts.</TRANSL>
